OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,407,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780578664
OL,3,CTube strike causes travel disruption
OL,4,Cacross London
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the mayor of London
OL,7,Fsaid: "Nobody wants to see strike
OL,8,Faction ` which has a serious impact on
OL,9,FLondoners, businesses and commuters.
OL,11,F"The mayor continues to urge the RMT
OL,12,Fand TfL to get around the table to
OL,13,Fresolve this matter, so we can avoid
OL,14,Ffurther disruption and keep London
OL,15,Fmoving."
OL,17,FFootfall in parts of London was down
OL,18,Fby 16% compared to a normal Tuesday
OL,19,Fmorning, according to data from Virgin
OL,20,FMedia O2.
OL,26,@oD@GOUsD@AOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
