PN,40607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780578664
OL,3,CTube strike causes travel disruption
OL,4,Cacross London
OL,6,FIts research showed a 16% fall in the
OL,7,FCity, 11% in Westminster, 8% in King's
OL,8,FCross and 6% in the West End.
OL,10,FA Virgin Media O2 spokesperson said:
OL,11,F"As Tube strikes take place across
OL,12,FLondon, our mobility data shows
OL,13,Ffootfall is down across some of the
OL,14,Fcity's busiest areas, including the
OL,15,FCity, Westminster and King's Cross.
OL,26,@sD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
