CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780578664
OL,3,CTube strike causes travel disruption
OL,4,Cacross London
OL,6,F"The figures provide a real-time
OL,7,Fsnapshot of how London responds when
OL,8,Fmajor transport disruption hits.
OL,9,FWhether people are working from home,
OL,10,Fchanging their commute or staying
OL,11,Fcloser to where they live, reliable
OL,12,Fmobile and broadband connectivity
OL,13,Fplays an increasingly important role
OL,14,Fin keeping people connected throughout
OL,15,Fthe day."
OL,17,FCommuters and other travellers were
OL,18,Falso hit by disruption to South
OL,19,FWestern Railway services on Tuesday
OL,20,Fmorning.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@IO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
