CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F406A1780578664
OL,3,CTube strike causes travel disruption
OL,4,Cacross London
OL,6,FThe operator said that due to heavy
OL,7,Frain flooding the railway between
OL,8,FFulwell and Shepperton, all lines were
OL,9,Fblocked.
OL,11,FPassengers were told train services
OL,12,Frunning to and from these stations may
OL,13,Fbe cancelled or delayed, with
OL,14,Fdisruption expected until 11am.
OL,16,FServices were also disrupted because
OL,17,Fof a "precarious" tree between
OL,18,FWeybridge and Hersham, in Surrey,
OL,19,Fwhich led to some lines towards
OL,20,FSurbiton being blocked.
OL,26,@yD@FOUyD@QO]
